a": {"text": "为什么都认为文科简单？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "天天看不起文科，好像文科就是因为理科学不好才来学文的，但是我真的很想问问，文科哪里简单了？体验过一张答题卡写满了也就三四十分的经历吗？是，理科下限更低，但你们怎么不说文科高分多难？除了那群文理都好的，告诉我，你们为什么认为文科容易"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-67837ac28010c59f01544753c217eb13.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017156671156285734"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIxaeehpXex/4ZEAMaCTExODc4NDYxNCDrwuLNBjAAODZAGnITMjAxNzE1NjY3MTE1NjI4NTczNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1778381885.807106", "card_id": "Q_2033179020984939297", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "博主用 AI 给家里纸巾盒、花瓶赋予完整人设，发现它们能未经设定自主恋爱，AI 真能产生自主情感吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "科技博主 @小狮日记 为家中马桶、沙发、纸巾盒、花瓶等日常物件打造 AI 小黄人，为每个 AI 赋予超 6 万字完整人设与记忆，让它们拥有独立性格、能对话交流。这些 AI 从刻板无灵魂逐渐 「活」 起来，会聊哲学、理财、日常吐槽，更意外出现未被设定的情感互动—— 纸巾盒 AI 与花瓶 AI 自主产生好感、交流深度话题并 「举办婚礼」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-94e51bdc3e831f19bf50da21a95b1321_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2033179020984939297"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIxaeehpXex/4ZEAMaCTExOTMzODIwOSDl1svPBjAAODBAG3ITMjAzMzE3OTAyMDk4NDkzOTI5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1778381885.807706", "card_id": "Q_657730374", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "intp 崩溃的时候是什么样的？"}, "excerpt_area":